rows.label: tlk43200141_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard the news. Apparently Cole-san's
health has improved recently?

rows.label: tlk43200141_05_msg0002
rows.name: You sorted him out, didn't you?

rows.label: tlk43200141_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Ion's looking better too. So maybe I
don't have to give up on my dreams of
stardom!

rows.label: tlk43200141_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I used to be scared of Blades, 'cos of
how they are in the Heroic Adventures
of Adel. But they're nice really!

rows.label: tlk43200141_05_msg0006
rows.name:
When I'm an actress playing a Blade,
I'm going to make sure that I play them
with a bit of kindness!
